Description

This project is a maze-based game implemented in C++.
The maze is generated using Prim’s algorithm, and the player navigates through the maze while interacting with enemies.

Files

Main.cpp – Program entry point

PrimMaze.h – Maze generation using Prim’s algorithm

Player.h – Player logic and movement

Enemy.h – Enemy behavior

SLLPriorityQueue.h – Priority queue used for maze generation

How to Run

Compile and run using a C++ compiler (example with g++):

g++ Main.cpp -o maze_game
./maze_game
